The Eps from e240 were all in flv format so I changed them with ERightSoft's SUPER to avi and tagged them with my name.

The quality is of a VHSRip I assume that recorded the show on FOX as you can see the Logo in the bottom right corner. It's not the best but it's watchable and if you're a George Carlin Fan, like I am, you won't mind.
